summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Plat 70E, page 168 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone certain property, located at the southwest corner of Detroit Avenue Southwest and Southwest Myrtle Street, extended, from Residential, Single Family 7200 (SF 7200) Zone to General Industrial (IG) Zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of TLC II Investors; C.F. No. 291561).
